	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have a Super Scope. But I don't have like 6 AA batteries handy. But I can assure you that only games that say Super Scope will work with it. And the only game I know of that uses a "standard" Lightgun is Lethal Enforcers which had the Justifier.
<br />
<br />It is important to point out that the Super Scope has more buttons, turbo fire, and a MUCH bigger lens which makes it ALOT more accurate than most lightguns. Not to mention the very handy scope sight.

		

